Pa kumbusha muakulu wa tumama, kumanya muakulu kampanda wa bena Lomo nekukuambuluishe bua kulonga Tshimputulukeshi bipepele.
Nansha nanku, bantu badi bamanye ndambu wa tshiena Espagne badi mua kumona ne: Tshimputulukeshi tshidi pabuipi menemene ne tshiena Espagne ne kabena ne bua kutshibala nkayabu to.
Nzubu ya dilamina bintu ya kale kayitu kabidi ya kuenza nayi mudimu dituku dionso to, idi ilua bilaminu bia bintu bia kale anyi miaba ya kulongela.
Mu tshikondo tshivua dinyanguka dia butoke kadiyi kabidi tshilumbu tshinene bu mudibi lelu, bavua batamba kubisangisha mu bimenga binene anyi mu bibambalu bia tulasa tua iniversite ne bivua bipepele bua kufikamu kupita mu nzubu ya matuku etu aa.
Telescope ya bungi ya matuku etu aa itu yenzela makebulula mu miaba ya kule idi ne kapepe kimpe.
Ditangila dia bilongo bia blé, didibu babikila ne: hanami, ndilue tshitupa tshia bilele bia bena Japon katshia mu bidimu bia nkama muanda mukulu.
Tshiambilu etshi tshivua tshifumine mu Chine tshikondo tshivua bilongo bia pome bitoloka bikole.
Mu Japon, amperere wakalongolola difesto dia kumpala dia bilongo bia fleurs de cerisiers anu buende yeye ne bua bantu bakuabu ba mu mulongo wa bantu banene ba mu lupangu lua amperere.
Mitshi idi ne bukole bua bungi bua kusomba mu muaba wa tshianana, nunku udi ne bua kukandamena diteta dia kuyumbusha, nansha wewe muikale mu tshitudilu tshimue tshia mâyi.
Wewe muye kuendakana mu lupangu lua manaya lua mbulamatadi, udi kabidi mua kuipatshibua mu lupangu lua manaya lua mbulamatadi.
Mu kuamba kuimpe , Singapour mmuaba udi kauyi njiwu ne mupepele bua kuendamu, muudi mua kusumba tshintu tshionso paudi ufikamu.
Pa mwanda wa kifuko kyadi'po kya "kulampe bininge na ekwatere" ku makilometele matyetye kete pa bukata bwa kungala ne kushika kwa ekwatere, byādi bimulomba kutanwa na byonso bibidi: kyanga kikatampe kya nyeke ne dyuba dikupakane (kutabukidila shi kūlu kudi biyampe).
Kudi kabidi bitanda bikuabu bidi bitangila ku Nord kua tshimenga tshia Hebelone, muaba wa tshilelelu wa kujiika bankambua ba mu Bible Abalahama, Izaka ne Yakoba ne ndelanganyi yabu.
Tangila ne: mashinyi audi uya nawu adi aya ku Yelushalema , ki nku tshimenga tshia bena Yuda tshia Kiriata-Arba tshidi pabuipi ne Akko to .
Dibue dia muinshi mua mâyi didi mua kuikala tshintu tshimpe tshia kudisha natshi nyama ya luonji.
Tshilejilu, udi mua kuya kumona nzubu minene ya mu tshibandabanda tshia Loire anyi tshia Rhine, kuya kuendakana mu bimenga binene bia ku musulu wa Danube, anyi kuenza luendu ne mazuwa ku tshisabu tshia Érié.
Njila ya mâyi ya muinshi mua buloba idi kabidi njila idi bantu batamba kuendela ne kuendela ku makalu.
Nowele ntshimue tshia ku bibilu binene bia bena Kristo, batu batshienza bua kusekelela diledibua dia Yezu.
Bantu badi kabayi bena Kristo ba mu matunga a bena Kristo ne ba mu matunga adi kaayi a bena Kristo mbangate bilele bia bungi bia mafesto.
Bamue bantu batu bamba ne: badi ne bua kushala batabale butuku bujima bua Pasaka too ne padiye ufua bua kumona mudi dîba dipatuka.
Tshilele etshi badi mua kutshiumvuija bilondeshile malu a teoloji a bena Kristo, kadi bidi bimueneka ne: tshivua tshilele tshia ntendelelu wa mu tshikondo tshia ku ntuadijilu kua muvu wa printemps ne tshia bufuke kumpala kua bena Kristo.
Mu bitanda bia bungi batu benza disambila dia kumpala kua Pasaka mu Disambombo dia ku ndekelu kua lumingu lua Pasaka, ne bantu batu batuadija kuenza masangisha bua kusekelela dibika dia Yezu ku lufu mundankulu.
Nyama yonso ivua mifike mu bidiila ebi ku ntuadijilu ivua mifike mu mâyi, mu ndeke anyi mu mâyi manene.
Bu mudibi kule ne buloba bunene, nyama idi idia nyama kayena mua kuenza luendu elu to, ke bualu kayi bivuba binene mbilue nyama minene idi idia nyama mu bidiila bia Galapagos.
Pavua bantu bafike mu Galapagos, bakatuadija kulela nyama mishilashilangane bu mudi mbuji, tubalu, ngombe, mpusu ne mbua.
Wewe muangate dipangadika dia kuya ku Nord-Ouest anyi ku Sud-Ouest mu tshikondo tshia mashika makole, udi mua kumona butuku bua ku Nord-Ouest, mbuena kuamba ne: dîba kadiena dianji kupatuka pa bule to.
Bualu ebu budi butupetesha mpunga muimpe wa kumona bukenke bua dîba.
Bu mudi miaba eyi kayiyi ne bantu ba bungi ne bu mudi butoke kabuyi buikale lutatu lua bungi, udi kabidi mua kubandila mitoto.
Bantu ba mu Japon batu ne bibidilu bia bungi bia malu a midimu kupita bantu ba ku Mputu.
Kumbele ndivuala dia pa tshibidilu dia bena mudimu, ne bena mudimu batu babikila bakuabu mu mêna abu a ku mudimu anyi a ku mudimu.
Buobumue mu mudimu budi ne mushinga wa bungi, bualu mudimu udi wenzeka mu tshibungi pamutu pa kuenzeka muntu pa nkayende.
Batu balomba bena mudimu bua batumikile mikenji ya bamfumu babu kakuyi dikokangana, ne misangu ya bungi batu balomba bamfumu babu bua bitabe mapangadika onso adibu bangata.
